create_time.description: The time when the EntryType was created.

effective_labels.description: All of labels (key/value pairs) present on the resource in GCP, including the labels configured through Terraform, other clients and services.

entry_type_id.description: The entry type id of the entry type.

labels.description: User-defined labels for the EntryType. **Note**: This field is non-authoritative, and will only manage the labels present in your configuration. Please refer to the field 'effective_labels' for all of the labels present on the resource.

location.description: The location where entry type will be created in.

name.description: The relative resource name of the EntryType, of the form: projects/{project_number}/locations/{location_id}/entryTypes/{entry_type_id}

platform.description: The platform that Entries of this type belongs to.

system.description: The system that Entries of this type belongs to.

terraform_labels.description: The combination of labels configured directly on the resource and default labels configured on the provider.

type_aliases.description: Indicates the class this Entry Type belongs to, for example, TABLE, DATABASE, MODEL.

uid.description: System generated globally unique ID for the EntryType. This ID will be different if the EntryType is deleted and re-created with the same name.

update_time.description: The time when the EntryType was last updated.

type.description: Required aspect type for the entry type.
